  "title": "Solution Architect",
  "description": "<p><strong>Primary Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Design overall system architecture for real-time transcription and translation platform</li>\n  <li>Define technical integration approach with existing audio-visual infrastructure</li>\n  <li>Establish security architecture framework to meet IM8 compliance requirements</li>\n  <li>Create scalable deployment strategy for on-premise infrastructure</li>\n  <li>Oversee technical feasibility assessment and risk mitigation strategies</li>\n  <li>Provide technical leadership and guidance to development team throughout POC implementation</li>\n  <li>Design data flow architecture for real-time processing and historical storage requirements</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Required Experience and Qualifications</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 8 years experience in enterprise solution architecture with focus on government systems</li>\n  <li>Proven track record with IM8 compliance implementation and security framework design</li>\n  <li>Extensive experience with Government Commercial Cloud (GCC) environments and hybrid cloud architectures</li>\n  <li>Deep understanding of real-time data processing systems and audio-visual integration technologies</li>\n  <li>Experience with transcription and translation technologies, AI/ML platforms</li>\n  <li>Demonstrated ability to work within government security protocols and requirements</li>\n</ul>",
